data.description:
Welcome to Chele Drive in the neighborhood of McClay Forest! The warmest 3 bedroom, 3
bathroom home located in unincorporated St Charles, conveniently surrounded by your
favorite local stores, restaurants, highways and one of the top rated school districts.
Walk into your cozy living room with a wood burning fireplace, eat-in kitchen with
stainless appliances and granite counter tops. Home features, newer roof, windows, water
heater, fresh neutral paint, insulated garage door, new interior doors, and privacy fence
surrounding your beautiful back yard where you can enjoy your morning coffee and patio
deck for afternoon grilling. Don't miss out on this updated move in ready home!
